                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 7.66,
                                "byte_start": 87124,
                                "byte_stop": 117844,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 88-42, Hallstrom versus Tillamook County will be announced by Justice O\u2019Connor."
